{"tid":604727,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳伊巴減薪95%投銀河","createTime":"2018-03-25T04:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T08:26:15.000Z","uid":4661,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7f4a9557c767dff506ffaa667461e35b9b8f94","tid":604727,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"為理念而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/392/20816071392/20829110259_600x337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F392%2F20816071392%2F20829110259_600x337.jpg&h=50898f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=rnLJWTJRiABdN9x9mvKqb2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9d76f37f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】神鋒伊巴謙莫域周五確定跟曼聯解約，加盟洛杉磯銀河，有傳減薪高達95%！<br />\n<br />\n美國《運動畫報（Sports Illustrated）》爆料，陣中已有3名特選球員杜斯山度士、莊拿芬杜斯山度士、阿歷辛迪尼的洛杉磯銀河，今次並不是以特選球只身份簽入伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）。<br />\n<br />\n因此，銀河在薪酬空間已不多的情況下，只能以目標分配資金（Targeted Allocation Money）給予伊巴年薪120萬歐元，跟他在曼聯的2180萬歐元相比，足足減薪95%！<br />\n<br />\n不過，36歲的伊巴現階段顯然不是為錢而戰：「經過在歐洲贏了33個冠軍，為多支世界上最佳球隊效力，跟多位世界最佳球員並肩，我希望去到英國踢出自己的足球，亦希望這裡的人可以享受我的足球。」"},{"pid":"2f5d435a69e91a90406a3458f94840b442ac27a2","tid":604727,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"篇野咁多錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d75d96155d2ed6ad983778ff8e78f5631fa26e","tid":604727,"uid":68916,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"120萬年薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揾得仲少過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0a92b26181930e8e67a29acbfa1346de47d0f1","tid":604727,"uid":114704,"like